# 🌐 Threat Intelligence Integration

## 🎯 Objective
Validate IOCs using external threat intelligence platforms.

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- VirusTotal
- AlienVault OTX API

## 🔍 IOC Validation

| Alert ID | IP            | Reputation        | Notes                                      |
|----------|---------------|-------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| 003      | 185.220.101.1 | Malicious (OTX)   | Linked to suspicious domains and activity  |

## 🔬 Analysis
The IP was analyzed using OTX API and VirusTotal. It showed multiple malicious associations and suspicious infrastructure.

## 🧠 Summary
Threat intelligence confirmed the IP as malicious. This enrichment validated alerts and improved incident prioritization.

